org.eclipse.scada.vi.details.model

Interface View

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ViewImpl

    public interface View
    A representation of the model object 'View'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Header Component
    • Groups
    • Hidden Component
    • Script Module
    • Tab Style

    See Also:
    DetailViewPackage.getView()
